connecting: |
  Opening WalletConnect.
  Scan the QR code with your wallet app.
  Your keys stay on your device — always.

disconnecting: |
  Disconnecting your wallet.
  You can reconnect anytime. Your funds are safe on-chain.

connected: |
  Wallet connected: {{address}}.
  Ready to trade non-custodial on multiple chains.

not_connected: |
  No wallet connected yet.
  Say "connect wallet" to start trading.
  Remember, your keys stay on your device.
